      <title>萨默斯：美联储已从严重的通胀错误中恢复过来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/summers-fed-recovered-from-egregious-inflation-mistake-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前财政部长、《华尔街周刊》撰稿人劳伦斯·萨默斯表示，美联储不应该对导致 2021 年通胀的供给侧冲击感到意外，但赞扬了鲍威尔主席在货币政策失误的情况下实现复苏。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/summers-fed-recovered-from-egregious-inflation-mistake-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 22:37:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>取消税收上调后标普将肯尼亚评级进一步下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/s-p-cuts-kenya-deeper-into-junk-after-repeal-of-tax-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在肯尼亚政府取消了旨在解决财政失衡问题的有争议的增税措施后，标准普尔全球评级将肯尼亚的信用评分进一步下调至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/s-p-cuts-kenya-deeper-into-junk-after-repeal-of-tax-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 21:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
